{"data":{"pagesYaml":{"intro":"Cannabis is your passion. Accounting is our specialty. Whether it is bookkeeping, tax preparation, or audits - we are here to help.","services_list":[{"title":"Income Tax preparation ","subtitle":"CANNABIS, HEMP, AND INDIVIDUALS","desc":"We provide tax preparation services for Cannabis start ups and their owners. We focus on Section 280 E mitigation and make sure that no possible deduction is missed. We also provide tax planning and instruct on forms that typically do not need our assistance, such as form 8300. ","service_image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/fdac6ef5e18ef6263a7bef090d84470c/f836f/irs-cannabis-icon.jpg","srcSet":"/static/fdac6ef5e18ef6263a7bef090d84470c/2c7f8/irs-cannabis-icon.jpg 50w,\n/static/fdac6ef5e18ef6263a7bef090d84470c/86e11/irs-cannabis-icon.jpg 100w,\n/static/fdac6ef5e18ef6263a7bef090d84470c/f836f/irs-cannabis-icon.jpg 200w,\n/static/fdac6ef5e18ef6263a7bef090d84470c/9dc27/irs-cannabis-icon.jpg 300w,\n/static/fdac6ef5e18ef6263a7bef090d84470c/2244e/irs-cannabis-icon.jpg 400w,\n/static/fdac6ef5e18ef6263a7bef090d84470c/49b36/irs-cannabis-icon.jpg 512w","srcWebp":"/static/fdac6ef5e18ef6263a7bef090d84470c/61e93/irs-cannabis-icon.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/fdac6ef5e18ef6263a7bef090d84470c/f6b6d/irs-cannabis-icon.webp 50w,\n/static/fdac6ef5e18ef6263a7bef090d84470c/d1f52/irs-cannabis-icon.webp 100w,\n/static/fdac6ef5e18ef6263a7bef090d84470c/61e93/irs-cannabis-icon.webp 200w,\n/static/fdac6ef5e18ef6263a7bef090d84470c/403a4/irs-cannabis-icon.webp 300w,\n/static/fdac6ef5e18ef6263a7bef090d84470c/1f5c5/irs-cannabis-icon.webp 400w,\n/static/fdac6ef5e18ef6263a7bef090d84470c/a3e81/irs-cannabis-icon.webp 512w","sizes":"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px"}}}},{"title":"Local Tax Compliance","subtitle":"EXCISE, CULTIVATION, SUT AND CANNABIS CITY TAX RETURNS","desc":"With us, you will not worry about missing a deadline for Excise or City tax. We research local guidance, prepare your tax return, and make sure you pay it on time. If needed, we will contact local authorities to sort out a notice in the mail or previous delinquency. We also take care of yearly business personal property and environmental fee returns. ","service_image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/c6d7fa8be8e05f89308e1efc43a42425/f836f/2.jpg","srcSet":"/static/c6d7fa8be8e05f89308e1efc43a42425/2c7f8/2.jpg 50w,\n/static/c6d7fa8be8e05f89308e1efc43a42425/86e11/2.jpg 100w,\n/static/c6d7fa8be8e05f89308e1efc43a42425/f836f/2.jpg 200w,\n/static/c6d7fa8be8e05f89308e1efc43a42425/9dc27/2.jpg 300w,\n/static/c6d7fa8be8e05f89308e1efc43a42425/2244e/2.jpg 400w,\n/static/c6d7fa8be8e05f89308e1efc43a42425/49b36/2.jpg 512w","srcWebp":"/static/c6d7fa8be8e05f89308e1efc43a42425/61e93/2.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/c6d7fa8be8e05f89308e1efc43a42425/f6b6d/2.webp 50w,\n/static/c6d7fa8be8e05f89308e1efc43a42425/d1f52/2.webp 100w,\n/static/c6d7fa8be8e05f89308e1efc43a42425/61e93/2.webp 200w,\n/static/c6d7fa8be8e05f89308e1efc43a42425/403a4/2.webp 300w,\n/static/c6d7fa8be8e05f89308e1efc43a42425/1f5c5/2.webp 400w,\n/static/c6d7fa8be8e05f89308e1efc43a42425/a3e81/2.webp 512w","sizes":"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px"}}}},{"title":"Bookkeeping","subtitle":"CANNABIS AND HEMP","desc":"Cannabis bookkeeping can get quite complicated. If you want those deductions on your tax return, you need to make sure that your accounting is GAAP compliant. Have you heard of such things as the Absorption method, Accrual accounting, and Lower of Cost or Market rule? If not, it's OK because we know what those mean, and we will make sure you are in compliance. ","service_image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/02aab053c50fc5251e036bdb9f617b8f/f836f/1.jpg","srcSet":"/static/02aab053c50fc5251e036bdb9f617b8f/2c7f8/1.jpg 50w,\n/static/02aab053c50fc5251e036bdb9f617b8f/86e11/1.jpg 100w,\n/static/02aab053c50fc5251e036bdb9f617b8f/f836f/1.jpg 200w,\n/static/02aab053c50fc5251e036bdb9f617b8f/9dc27/1.jpg 300w,\n/static/02aab053c50fc5251e036bdb9f617b8f/2244e/1.jpg 400w,\n/static/02aab053c50fc5251e036bdb9f617b8f/49b36/1.jpg 512w","srcWebp":"/static/02aab053c50fc5251e036bdb9f617b8f/61e93/1.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/02aab053c50fc5251e036bdb9f617b8f/f6b6d/1.webp 50w,\n/static/02aab053c50fc5251e036bdb9f617b8f/d1f52/1.webp 100w,\n/static/02aab053c50fc5251e036bdb9f617b8f/61e93/1.webp 200w,\n/static/02aab053c50fc5251e036bdb9f617b8f/403a4/1.webp 300w,\n/static/02aab053c50fc5251e036bdb9f617b8f/1f5c5/1.webp 400w,\n/static/02aab053c50fc5251e036bdb9f617b8f/a3e81/1.webp 512w","sizes":"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px"}}}},{"title":"Point of Sale Software","subtitle":"CANNABIS DISPENSARIES","desc":"CDTFA wants its share of Excise and SUT tax. If you under collected, the agency will ask you to pay the missing tax out of pocket. If you over-collected, the agency will want this money too! As a dispensary you collect those taxes through your Point of Sale System, and very often, its tax settings are incorrect. We help you set up your POS tax withholdings; this way, you do not pay a dime less or more in tax. ","service_image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/29ca9e2311ca2d824afd5e548f8afdfd/f836f/point-of-sale-software.jpg","srcSet":"/static/29ca9e2311ca2d824afd5e548f8afdfd/2c7f8/point-of-sale-software.jpg 50w,\n/static/29ca9e2311ca2d824afd5e548f8afdfd/86e11/point-of-sale-software.jpg 100w,\n/static/29ca9e2311ca2d824afd5e548f8afdfd/f836f/point-of-sale-software.jpg 200w,\n/static/29ca9e2311ca2d824afd5e548f8afdfd/9dc27/point-of-sale-software.jpg 300w,\n/static/29ca9e2311ca2d824afd5e548f8afdfd/2244e/point-of-sale-software.jpg 400w,\n/static/29ca9e2311ca2d824afd5e548f8afdfd/49b36/point-of-sale-software.jpg 512w","srcWebp":"/static/29ca9e2311ca2d824afd5e548f8afdfd/61e93/point-of-sale-software.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/29ca9e2311ca2d824a